{"tid":619984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【扑頭黨出沒】兩賊鐵通扑頭 當街搶途人金頸鏈","createTime":"2018-04-07T07:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T07:50:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"564f08c12ebd25bbd64cb5e05dd3216bb263041d","tid":619984,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180407/58043092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180407%2F58043092&d=lRYOs8fSOO9nUw%2FeNYAX1ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=152bc40d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180407%2F58043092&h=08d271fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180407/58043092</a><br />\n<br />\n【扑頭黨出沒】兩賊鐵通扑頭 當街搶途人金頸鏈<br />\n<br />\n即時突發  2018-04-07 00:33:55 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n昨晚10時許，一名姓陸62歲男子，行經牛頭角上邨常興樓對開時，被兩名持鐵通賊人截劫，向他扑頭襲擊，企圖搶他一條約值3萬元金頸鏈，事主反抗與賊人糾纏。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，雙方互相拉扯，金頸鏈被扯斷，賊人掠去半條值1萬5千元金頸鏈，事主力保另外半條。警方接報到場，附近兜截沒有發現，事主頭部受傷，送院治理。現正追緝兩名20至30歲、身高1.6及1.7米、穿著深色及淺色風褸男子。<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 即Call《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 ：63836568<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180407/large/1523073321_37d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180407%2Flarge%2F1523073321_37d6.jpg&h=7f325dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180407/large/1523035682_f0ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180407%2Flarge%2F1523035682_f0ea.jpg&h=a07c9f89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遇劫頭部受傷男子送院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180407/large/1523048833_9ea7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180407%2Flarge%2F1523048833_9ea7.jpg&h=8ca79425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劫案現場牛頭角上邨常興樓。(唐家輝攝)"},{"pid":"c3b970b0df1782164ba8d5bd04a77aa4b6fb1b13","tid":619984,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:28:00.000Z","msg":"通常都係大陸人多"},{"pid":"81278e9972d78c02f8fa08f9ba887313cc71b147","tid":619984,"uid":56561,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:45:35.000Z","msg":"廢中廢老鍾意掛金上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3f774c56f5a71ae5db1d303c2b94fc9b532606","tid":619984,"uid":169468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:50:13.000Z","msg":"身高1.6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}